metadata.name: Extension of Man (2023) #1
metadata.description:
"Extension of Man" is a series of machine-interpreted artworks built upon handcrafted metaglass voxel imagery by JYD. The pieces feature a collection of geometric glyphs of metaglass, a voxel-based medium unique to previous works published on Tezos.

The use of machine interpretation adds an abstraction of artificial intelligence to the original genesis work, which is processed until the underlying message is lost (and remains known only to JYD).
